sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    User ->> AuthenticationController: POST /api/v1/auth/password/forgot/request
    AuthenticationController ->> PasswordService: requestPasswordResetOtp(identifier, identifierType)
    PasswordService -->> AuthenticationController: completion
    AuthenticationController -->> User: 200 ApiResponse {message: "If an account exists, you’ll receive reset instructions."}
